Find the LCD for the fractions

\dfrac{7}{8} - \dfrac{1}{6}

\dfrac{52}{75} + \dfrac{13}{24}

Find the LCD for the fractions

\dfrac{3}{4a^2b^2} + \dfrac{7}{10ab^3}

\dfrac{3}{8t^4} - \dfrac{3}{5t^2}

Write an equivalent fraction with the new denominator.

\dfrac{1}{n} = \dfrac{?}{n^2-n}

\dfrac{4}{a-1} = \dfrac{?}{a^2-1}

Write an equivalent fraction with the new denominator.

\dfrac{b}{b-2} = \dfrac{?}{(b+3)(b-2)}

\dfrac{x-1}{x^2+2x} = \dfrac{?}{(x^2-x)(x+2)}
